---
title: Cheat's Moroccan Pork Tagine with Mint Couscous & Toasted Almonds
description: Take a little bit of refreshing mint, add a little almondy crunch, a dash of mango chutney for sweetness and what have you got? Why, it’s the perfect recipe for a delicious cheat's Moroccan pork tagine!
